title: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Sweden Points of Interest, Sweden, 2008

features.name: Max i Lund, Kung Oscars väg 14

name: Openstreetmap Geofabrik, Sweden Points of Interest, Sweden, 2008
description: This data set shows points of interest in Sweden. Features included in this data set include, libraries, post offices, places of worship, parking, restaurants, cafes, fuel, parking, police, theaters, cinemas, prisons, universities, camp sites and other public places. there are over 4,000 points of interest included.
